(34, 71, 2, 'Home Loan Sales Executive / Sales Manager', 'Delhi', 'Confidencial', 'Rs. 30,000 - Rs. 40,000', 150, NULL, NULL, 'Any', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Full-time', 'About the Role:\r\n\r\nWe are looking for a dynamic and result-driven Home Loan Sales Executive to join our growing team. The candidate will be responsible for sourcing, explaining, and closing home loan deals by connecting with potential customers and channel partners.\r\n\r\nKey Responsibilities:\r\nGenerate leads through open market, referrals, and builders\r\nBuild strong relationships with real estate agents, builders & DSAs\r\nExplain home loan products, interest rates, and eligibility criteria to customers\r\nGuide clients through the complete loan process (documentation to disbursal)\r\nMeet monthly sales targets and ensure business growth\r\nMaintain follow-ups and customer satisfaction\r\nCoordinate with banks/NBFCs for smooth loan processing\r\n\r\nRequirements:\r\nGraduation in any field\r\nGood communication & convincing skills\r\nSales-oriented mindset with target-driven approach\r\nFreshers with strong interest in sales can apply\r\nPrior experience in banking, NBFC, or loan sales is a plus\r\n\r\nSalary & Benefits:\r\nFixed Salary + Attractive Incentives\r\nPerformance-based growth opportunities\r\nTraining & career development support\r\n\r\nPreferred Candidates:\r\nExperience in Home Loan / Mortgage / LAP sales\r\nStrong local market knowledge\r\nImmediate joiners preferred', 2, 7, 'Direct Sales', '2026-09-30', 'https://simplyhiree.com/', 'pending_approval', 'all', '2026-03-29 12:53:49', '2026-03-29 12:54:26', NULL, 3),
