(36, NULL, 3, 'Freelance Recruiter', 'Pan India', 'Simplyhiree', NULL, 25, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0.00, 30, NULL, 'Full-time', 'Freelance Recruiter | Work From Home\r\n\r\nCompany: Simply Hiree\r\nJob Type: Freelance / Remote / Commission-Based\r\nEarning Potential: ₹10,000 – ₹1,00,000+ per month 💰\r\n\r\n🔥 About Simply Hiree\r\n\r\nSimply Hiree is a fast-growing staffing & recruitment marketplace helping companies hire faster across India across bulk, mid & leadership hiring.\r\n\r\n💼 Role Overview\r\n\r\nWe are hiring Freelance Recruiters / HR Recruiters who want to work from home and earn unlimited incentives by closing positions across multiple industries.\r\n\r\n🎯 Responsibilities\r\nUnderstand client hiring requirements\r\nSource candidates via own database, job portals & social media\r\nScreen & shortlist candidates\r\nSchedule interviews & coordinate with clients\r\nFollow-up till candidate joining\r\n\r\n💰 Earnings Structure\r\n💵 Per joining payout (₹2,000 – ₹20,000 per closure)\r\n🎯 No salary cap – unlimited earning potential\r\n🏆 Top performers earn ₹50K – ₹1 Lakh/month\r\n\r\n✅ Mandatory Requirements\r\n🔥 Own candidate database (must have active pool of candidates)\r\nMinimum 6 months recruitment experience preferred\r\n💻 Laptop + stable internet connection\r\nKnowledge of Naukri, Indeed, LinkedIn sourcing\r\nStrong communication & follow-up skills\r\n\r\n🌟 Why Join Simply Hiree?\r\n🏠 100% Work from home\r\n⏰ Flexible working hours\r\n📈 Access to multiple active requirements\r\n🤝 Dedicated support team\r\n💸 Fast payouts', 1, 10, 'Recruitment, HR, Hiring, Screening, Sourcing, Human Resorce', '2028-03-10', 'https://simplyhiree.com/', 'approved', 'all', '2026-04-10 04:39:23', '2026-04-10 04:39:23', NULL, 3);
